summary: An Ordinance authorizing the dismissal of a suit to condemn private property for the laying off, extending, opening and establishing of Fourteenth Avenue South from Greeley Street to the south line of Section 29, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W. M., as provided under Ordinance No. 33445, Cause No. 107445, insofar as the same affects certain property in tracts "D" and "E", Queen Supplemental Addition to the City of Seattle, and in Section 29, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W. M., and authorizing the payment of all taxable costs incurred by the owners of said property in said condemnation proceedings, and appropriating money therefor.
